        Constructor for a new RoleMember. Will by default be constructed with the primary key 0, which means that this object hasn't been persisted yet. In that case, the primary key will be set by the CRUD bean.
        Parameters:
        tokenType - Type
        tokenIssuerId - the issuer identifier of this token or 0 if not relevant
        tokenMatchKey - Key
        tokenMatchOperator - Operator
        tokenMatchValue - the actual value with which to match
        roleId - roleId the ID of the role to which this member belongs. May be null.
        description - a human readable description of this role member.
